com.vaadin.ui.videojs

Class VideojsPlayerState

  • java.lang.Object
    • JavaScriptComponentState
      • com.vaadin.ui.videojs.VideojsPlayerState

  • public class VideojsPlayerState
extends JavaScriptComponentState
    Shared state object The basic communication from a server-side VideojsPlayer to its the client-side widget counterpart is handled using a VideojsPlayerState. The VideojsPlayerState is serialized transparently. VideojsPlayerState should be considered read-only on the client-side, as VideojsPlayerState is not serialized back to the server-side. VaadiProject 2013
    Author:
    Juha Mäkilä and Sami Holck
